com.chute.sdk.v2.model

Class AlbumModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chute.sdk.v2.model.AlbumModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class AlbumModel
extends Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Albums represent a collection of assets which can be created by a single user, viewed by everyone or privileged users. Each album contains links, counters, shortcut, name, which user it belongs to, media and comments moderators and time and date of creation.
